    "description": "Takachiho Co.,Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the wholesale of souvenirs in Japan. It operates through Souvenir Wholesale Business, Retail Business, Bath Facility Business, Real Estate Rental Business, Outdoor Equipment Business, and Other segments. The company manufactures and sells tourist souvenirs to hotels, accommodation facilities, souvenir shops at JR stations, and highway service areas, as well as through directly managed stores; manufactures confectioneries, including chocolate sandwich cookies, filled cookies and buns, and other cookies; leases real estate space at Shopping Town Aozora; manages retail stores under the syunsui brand; and operates public baths, as well as fruit, crepe, and curry restaurants. It also sells fishing and outdoor equipment through Outdoor Station Van Van retail stores. The company serves tourist souvenir shops, stores in commercial facilities, character shops, and baseball team shops. Takachiho Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1949 and is headquartered in Nagano, Japan."
